text:
Kylie Jenner has recently become a mom to baby Stormi Webster with boyfriend Travis Scott and she is also a businesswoman, thus the owner of her cosmetics company named after her “Kylie Cosmetics.” Besides all of these, it really looks that Kylie Jenner has mastered the art of selfies. The 20-years-old star can simply fill a book full of selfies.

Now, since June 21st is considered to be National Selfie Day we have no doubt, Kylie, is the Queen of selfies.

To see the proofs yourself, see 8 of her variety selfies game:

A post shared by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on May 27, 2018 at 10:55am PDT

The Bathroom Selfie: Of all types of Kardashian-Jenner selfies, the bathroom selfie is probably the most infamous.

A post shared by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Mar 10, 2018 at 10:19pm PST

The Sister Selfie: Talk about a family selfie! The Kardashian-Jenner sisters posed for a mirror selfie together.

A post shared by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Mar 10, 2018 at 3:43pm PST

The Closet Selfie: Showing off your fashion sense and your purse collection? Double win.

A post shared by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Feb 28, 2017 at 5:07pm PST

The Car Selfie: Taking a selfie on a long drive is a classic.

A post shared by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Jan 29, 2017 at 3:57pm PST

The Bikini Selfie: Body goals. Bikini goals. Everything goals. Goals goals!

A post shared by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Jun 10, 2018 at 11:38am PDT

The Mom Selfie: New moms have time for selfies too! Kylie shared this picture of herself while embracing the natural look and letting her freckles reveal themselves.

A post shared by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Jun 7, 2018 at 5:48pm PDT

The BFF Selfie: Friends who take a selfie together, stay together!

A post shared by Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Nov 4, 2017 at 8:49am PDT

The Snapchat Selfie: I guess I’m not the only one who loves to play around with the filters on Snapchat.
